<item>
            <title>[QPID-962] ConnectionTest takes too long to run</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPID-962</link>
                <project id="12310520" key="QPID">Qpid</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ConnectionTest takes 90-odd seconds to run, which is both frustrating and possibly indicative of a problem. Some investigation required.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
